      <title>はじまるよ~博客搭建日志 3</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/01/%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%81%BE%E3%82%8B%E3%82%88-3/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/01/%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%81%BE%E3%82%8B%E3%82%88-3/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>今天轮到我平泽忧扇<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/play/ep21265">巴掌</a>啦</p><span id="more"></span><!-- 简单示例 (id, server, type)  -->    <div id="aplayer-UUwsGzxp" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"         data-id="2420303" data-server="netease" data-type="album" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="340px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#ad7a86"    ></div><h2 id="代码首行缩进"><a href="#代码首行缩进" class="headerlink" title="代码首行缩进"></a>代码首行缩进</h2><p>昨天提到过这个问题</p><blockquote><p>但是又发现主题的代码框第一行存在一个空格的缩进，应该是个bug吧，提了issue希望能被修复。<br><img onerror="imgOnError(this);" data-fancybox="gallery" src="/%E6%9D%82%E5%9B%BE/1669792376204.jpg" alt="bug" data-caption="bug" loading="lazy"></p></blockquote><p>已经被人提过<a href="https://github.com/theme-nexmoe/hexo-theme-nexmoe/pull/246">pr解决了</a>，但是还没merge到release版本里，暂且手动修改下。</p><h2 id="建站时间"><a href="#建站时间" class="headerlink" title="建站时间"></a>建站时间</h2><p><a href="https://godweiyang.com/2018/04/13/hexo-blog/">这篇博文</a>有很多有用的东西，东拼西凑在网站左下角加了一条建站时间，只显示天数，不那么聒噪。</p><p>直接在包里面的<code>\layout\_partial\header.ejs</code>修改，在<code>&lt;div class=&quot;nexmoe-copyright&quot;&gt;</code>下直接加一句调用。</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">class</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;nexmoe-copyright&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 新增建站时间 --&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;sitetime&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">br</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>函数放在代码最后面就行</p><figure class="highlight reasonml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs reasonml">&lt;script language=javascript&gt;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> site<span class="hljs-constructor">Time()</span> &#123;<br>        window.set<span class="hljs-constructor">Timeout(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;siteTime()&quot;</span>, 1000)</span>;<br>        var days = <span class="hljs-number">1000</span><span class="hljs-operator"> * </span><span class="hljs-number">60</span><span class="hljs-operator"> * </span><span class="hljs-number">60</span><span class="hljs-operator"> * </span><span class="hljs-number">24</span>;<br>        var today = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-constructor">Date()</span>;<br>        var todayYear = today.get<span class="hljs-constructor">FullYear()</span>;<br>        var todayMonth = today.get<span class="hljs-constructor">Month()</span> + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        var todayDate = today.get<span class="hljs-constructor">Date()</span>;<br>        var todayHour = today.get<span class="hljs-constructor">Hours()</span>;<br>        var todayMinute = today.get<span class="hljs-constructor">Minutes()</span>;<br>        var todaySecond = today.get<span class="hljs-constructor">Seconds()</span>;<br>        var t1 = Date.<span class="hljs-constructor">UTC(2022, 11, 26, 13, 25, 22)</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">//对应北京时间2022-11-26 21:25:22</span><br>        var t2 = Date.<span class="hljs-constructor">UTC(<span class="hljs-params">todayYear</span>, <span class="hljs-params">todayMonth</span>, <span class="hljs-params">todayDate</span>, <span class="hljs-params">todayHour</span>, <span class="hljs-params">todayMinute</span>, <span class="hljs-params">todaySecond</span>)</span>;<br>        var diff = t2 - t1;<br>        var diffDays = <span class="hljs-module-access"><span class="hljs-module"><span class="hljs-identifier">Math</span>.</span></span>floor(diff<span class="hljs-operator"> / </span>days);<br>        document.get<span class="hljs-constructor">ElementById(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;sitetime&quot;</span>)</span>.innerHTML = diffDays + <span class="hljs-string">&quot; days traveling&quot;</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    site<span class="hljs-constructor">Time()</span>;<br>&lt;/script&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="评论系统"><a href="#评论系统" class="headerlink" title="评论系统"></a>评论系统</h2><p>想找一个不用登录就能用的，只有valine，但是样式实在是太丑了。基于github的又只能github登录，矮子里面拔将军选了disqus。<br>主题的文档里评论接口还是<code>comment</code>，最新版本已经改成<code>slotComment</code>了，一样配置貌似就不能用了？暂且继续蒙古里。</p><h2 id="访问统计"><a href="#访问统计" class="headerlink" title="访问统计"></a>访问统计</h2><p>这个接口也一样，貌似在新版本里被废弃了，所以尝试在<code>\layout\layout.ejs</code>的<code>&lt;head&gt;</code>后面直接添加google跟踪代码，测试有效。</p><p>并且通过google analytics认证的网站会同时被google索引，不用再添加认证。</p><p>百度只添加了索引的代码，同样的位置，也成功被索引。</p><h2 id="Task-list"><a href="#Task-list" class="headerlink" title="Task list"></a>Task list</h2><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>代码高亮：有点问题，暂且蒙古里（虽然我并一定会写很多代码</del><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>首行缩进</del></li></ul></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>social模块：</del><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>这个主题我唯一想换掉的就是左下角github的图标，太憨憨了（文档提供了方法</del></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>一些额外的个人链接想要加上，要摸索下</del></li></ul></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>建站时间</del></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>网站索引：要去google和baidu上登记一下（争取一点微弱的曝光量</del></li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> <del>访问统计：在加了在加了，虽然只有自己刷刷数据（悲）。</del></li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 本地搜索：可能会加？也可能懒得弄了</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 关于博主：可能这个模块才是比较重要的吧，有点懒，想写成CV的样子又觉得该随意点</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 个人域名：又要花钱，花钱的事最后再说</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Latex支持：latex公式写着很有意思，虽然我肯定不会在博客写，但说不定会装上</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 评论插件：感觉都不好用，可能不会装</li></ul><p>最近要忙论文了，之后再说啦，<em>じゃあね~</em></p><div align="center">    <img src="https://tskun.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/byebye_girl.png"    alt="挥挥"></img></div>]]></content>
      
      
